## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6aae5-102">控件允许以编程方式访问服务器上`link`的 HTML 元素。 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6aae5-102">The <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink> control allows programmatic access to the HTML `link` element on the server.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6aae5-103"><xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink>控件可用于以编程方式在网页中指定级联样式表 (CSS) 引用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6aae5-103">The <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink> control can be used to programmatically specify a cascading style sheet (CSS) reference in a Web page.</span></span>  
  
   
  
