 <span data-ttu-id="6aae5-105">若要运行前面的代码示例, 需要一个名为`Stylesheet.css`的级联样式表 (CSS), 其中包含以下代码, 并保存在与您的网站相同的目录中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6aae5-105">To run the preceding code example, you need a cascading style sheet (CSS) named `Stylesheet.css`, containing the following code, saved in the same directory as your Web site.</span></span>  
  
